{"tid":2388810,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「狗狗幣」價格倍數急升　Robinhood 決定限制其交易","createTime":"2021-01-31T11:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T14:13:33.000Z","uid":66271,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"faaf6102d6ca566e23fde0b154aad9d7eefa7c0f","tid":2388810,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/5a558ea7d3806c0b44860f07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F5a558ea7d3806c0b44860f07.jpg&h=a8ff8d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近美國股市投資氣氛變得相當熱烈，GME 的散戶大戰做空機構事件最近蔓延到加密貨幣，其中「狗狗幣」Dogecoin 價格因此倍數急升，而投資平台 Robinhood 就決定限制其交易嘗試降溫。<br />\n<br />\nGME 事件令不少投資者對於股市失去信心，開始將投資轉移到加密貨幣，Dogecoin 就成為了波幅最大的加密貨幣之一，在 24 小時內已經急升 3 倍，而且最高位接近 8 倍，猶如坐過山車。Robinhood 作為其中一個美國最普及的股票和加密貨幣投資平台，就表示「由於市場出現異常情況，已經暫時停止使用『即時購買力』資金購買加密貨幣，只可以用已結算資金購買，未來會繼續留意市場情況繼續與顧客溝通。」<br />\n<br />\nDogecoin 是在 2013 年開始流通，最初只是基於一個 meme 所開發的加密貨幣，並沒有什麼宏大的願景，但在幾年間一直都是最受歡迎的加密貨幣之一。而 Robinhood 之前因為限制用家購買 GME 股票，已經引起了 Google Play Store 劣評潮，但 Google 後來幫他們刪除了接近 10 萬個負評令用家更加不滿。今次事件會否再令不滿情況火上加油？"},{"pid":"da832fb53d4a11bd8ca02db7cbcd85de065d8499","tid":2388810,"uid":522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"又準備推doge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd9353a99897422a362979f75e7e78d0b3de8a2","tid":2388810,"uid":82359,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"如果可以用dogecoin買Tesla....."},{"pid":"7fa43c40d61eb07b678f50b5d3e0dd27cde70ebb","tid":2388810,"uid":72354,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da832fb53d4a11bd8ca02db7cbcd85de065d8499","tid":2388810,"uid":522,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"又準備推doge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"牛牛都買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc08d270ee4c496b54b03845c7934455395ed50","tid":2388810,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"等執笠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9818bdd319f39f02482b4e05af514f6ea35f30","tid":2388810,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"一升就限制交易<br />\n咁tsla果d又唔限？"},{"pid":"7e4da0b1e613aee275ffeb69f1139285d492e3ac","tid":2388810,"uid":52939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:00:21.000Z","msg":"今日買狗幣 <br />\n聽日勝首期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439804ae5b056336e223bb070fe2ffb8499318f5","tid":2388810,"uid":220368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"點樣買架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea1d2512411d63e07a2fede66cfb3e2ad823919","tid":2388810,"uid":346404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:10:29.000Z","msg":"大戶仲未入市，壓住個升勢先"},{"pid":"5e20e6e1209d0359a452224d62bcb30ae0473e71","tid":2388810,"uid":125670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:40:46.000Z","msg":"有無狗幣概念股？"},{"pid":"723d7983e1cdde9d4978f61332492cfcfee21ca6","tid":2388810,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3da035d19d9588afe513f861f8e95ed78d2b79","tid":2388810,"uid":186543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"